title: Indie-Rock Band Whirr Addresses the Outrage and Fallout Over Transphobic Tweets
text:
Indie-Rock Band Whirr Addresses the Outrage, and Fallout, Over Transphobic Tweets 
Billboard Biz Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Whirr posted, in reference to a hardcore punk group from Olympia, Washington, "Lol @ G.L.O.S.S." When others came to the defense of G.L.O.S.S., which has multiple transgender members,...
